    <h1>How to Play UNO Online</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">A step-by-step guide to playing UNO in your browser with friends.</p>

    <h2>Step 1: Enter a Nickname</h2>
    <p>Go to the <a href="/play">Play page</a> and type your nickname. This is what other players will see during the game. You can use up to 16 characters.</p>

    <h2>Step 2: Create or Join a Room</h2>
    <p><strong>Create a Room:</strong> Click "Create New Room" to start a new game. You'll become the host and receive a room code (like UNO-ABCD). Toggle "Private Room" if you only want people with the link to join.</p>
    <p><strong>Join a Room:</strong> Enter a room code shared by a friend, or click "Browse Public Rooms" to find open games.</p>

    <h2>Step 3: Invite Friends</h2>
    <p>Share the room code or click "Copy Invite Link" to send a direct link. Friends can join from any device — phone, tablet, or computer.</p>

    <h2>Step 4: Start the Game</h2>
    <p>The host clicks "Start Game" once at least 2 players have joined. Each player receives 7 cards, and a card is flipped to start the discard pile.</p>

    <h2>Step 5: Play Cards</h2>
    <p>On your turn, click a card that matches the top of the discard pile by color, number, or symbol. If you can't play, click the draw pile to draw a card. After drawing, you can play the drawn card or pass.</p>

    <h2>Step 6: Call UNO!</h2>
    <p>When you have 1 card left, press the UNO button quickly! If another player catches you first, you'll draw 2 penalty cards.</p>

    <h2>Step 7: Win!</h2>
    <p>The first player to play all their cards wins. The host can start a new game immediately.</p>

    <h2>Tips for New Players</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Save your Wild and +4 cards for when you really need them</li>
      <li>Pay attention to what colors other players are low on</li>
      <li>Don't forget to call UNO — the penalty is harsh!</li>
      <li>Read the full <a href="/rules">UNO Rules</a> for detailed card descriptions</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="cta-banner">
      <h3>Ready to Try?</h3>
      <p>Start your first game in under 10 seconds.</p>
      <a href="/play" class="btn btn-hero">Play Now — Free</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
